{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-caofeng-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-caofeng-001", "source_id": "guofeng-caofeng-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·曹風·001.1", "text_original": "蜉蝣之羽，衣裳楚楚。心之憂矣，於我歸處。", "text_normalized": "蜉蝣之羽，衣裳楚楚。心之憂矣，於我歸處。", "notes": "蜉蝣 Chinese stanza 1."}
